# The fail2ban container writes runtime state into config/ on natto
# (fail2ban.sqlite3, the image's generated jail.local, action.d/, logs).
# Only our two hand-written rule files are version-controlled; everything
# else under config/ is container-generated and must never be committed.
config/*
!config/fail2ban/
config/fail2ban/*
!config/fail2ban/filter.d/
!config/fail2ban/jail.d/
config/fail2ban/filter.d/*
config/fail2ban/jail.d/*
!config/fail2ban/filter.d/jellyfin.conf
!config/fail2ban/jail.d/jellyfin.conf
